items.checkin_comment: Orange marmalade, candied orange, lemon, grapefruit peel, faint candyish orange lollipop, fruity yeast aroma with a mild fruity floral, citrus, herbal hop nose and a fruity toasted, bready, pale malt faint candied grapefruit, orange peel, citrus hop taste

user.bio: [Bière, beer, öl]   I am a beer trotter! Love beers from around the world. Making my own beer, kombucha and sake too!
Real human man likes doing real human things like consuming the flesh of animals, breathing oxygen and walking on leg.
Beer, whiskey and coffee are my loves! I use the uni scoring system for my ratings, and love both strong and light beers
